    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, this example has undergone subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS system overhaul, addressing the chassis and timing vulnerabilities inherent to the platform. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the paint exhibits minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the engine compression is within factory spec and the valve clearances have been recently adjusted. A solid, technically-sorted specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
